data.text:
Post by huskervolleyfan14 on

With athletes in the 2025 class now being able to commit, I figured I would start a thread to keep track of all the commits that come in! Everyone deserves recognition so if you see a commitment to any D1 school before I do, please feel free to shout them out in this thread! I will make sure to keep updating the original post so that the list is easily accessible. Thanks in advance for all of the help over the next 2 years!
